{
  "stem": "8212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And when I came to Lyon, I wanted to draw or do something like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And somebody got me a job in a place that was painting silk scarves by hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, this was a place-- painting silk scarves, you had the silk flat on a long, long table.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There were two pieces of wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The silk was nailed to it and the middle was very flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there was just a little bit of white, flat white, indicating the motifs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And you were supposed to paint flowers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We made beautiful-- I still have one of those scarves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We did beautiful scarves, and there were like three people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So one of them did the reds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "One of them did the pinks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "One of them did the green leaves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then we went back, and that's how we finished it, one thing after another after it dried.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But it was also a terrible place, because it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And that's the first time in my life I saw rats.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "It was full of rats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And in order to work there, you kept seeing them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "You always went [STOMPING FEET] with your legs just to make a lot of noise so they would disappear.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They were pretty awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Well, I worked there 'til 1942 when we heard that France was going to be annexed, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Half of France was Vichy France, and the other part was still libre, free.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But it was going to be annexed, and this was in September, 1942.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I mean, this story repeats itself continuously.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We packed again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We took a train.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went towards the Swiss border, to hopefully go into Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With us was my mother's brother and his wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had no children.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
